==English==
===Etymology===
for [[w:Louis de Broglie|Louis de Broglie]]
===Noun phrase===
'''[[De Broglie]] [[wavelength]]'''
#{{physics}} the wavelength, λ=h/p, associated with a [[beam]] of [[particle]]s of [[momentum]] p. (h being [[Planck's constant]].) The same [[formula]] gives the momentum of a [[photon]] or wavelength λ.
[[Category:English eponyms]]

